                            <comment id="14681138" author="jahewson" created="Tue, 11 Aug 2015 02:45:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This file contains a PFB font with invalid charstrings. The charstrings are completely invalid, essentially nonsense.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14681295" author="tilman" created="Tue, 11 Aug 2015 06:11:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reopening - the latest change prevents the file bugzilla867751.pdf from being rendered correctly, see page 35, the &quot;special&quot; glyphs are now missing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14681299" author="tilman" created="Tue, 11 Aug 2015 06:16:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Other affected files: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1691&quot; title=&quot;&amp;quot;Foreign&amp;quot; characters are not rendered&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1691&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1691&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-FORIS-HV.pdf (p2++), pdfbox-1809.pdf, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2192&quot; title=&quot;&amp;quot;unknown command&amp;quot; in Type1CharString.handleCommand&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2192&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2192&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-006972.pdf (p21). I stopped after that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14692811" author="jahewson" created="Wed, 12 Aug 2015 02:37:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hmm... thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
